{"tid":446731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"官中停課直播睇李飛 中學生被邀請自願收看","createTime":"2017-10-24T14:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T16:42:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e77cf3eefde024fcd0b876e2f623e39f9f218bc1","tid":446731,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171024/large/1508848702_cf3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171024%2Flarge%2F1508848702_cf3c.jpg&h=eca40435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局於下月16日，在灣仔會展舉辦「香港特別行政區成立二十周年《基本法》研討會」，屬回歸20週年活動之一。《香港01》報道指，部分官立中學當日將取消2節課，集體收看研討會直播；教育局發言人回覆時承認，將配合是次活動，已邀請各辦學團體安排屬下中學師生在校內觀看直播，並鼓勵官立學校作相應安排。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，邀請中學生收看直播，是為了增進學生認識「一國兩制」及《基本法》。學校的參與純屬自願性質，有關的實際安排最終由學校決定。<br />\n根據「慶祝香港特別行政區成立20周年」網頁資料，《基本法》研討會將在灣仔會展舉辦，活動內容為「邀請專家和嘉賓就20年來香港成功落實《基本法》和「一國兩制」的議題發表意見」，但並沒有列出嘉賓名單。《香港01》報道指，全國人大常委會副秘書長、基本法委員會主任李飛將進行主題演講，行政長官林鄭月娥則會致開幕辭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171024/57372736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F57372736&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=cc66301a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F57372736&h=b0096cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171024/57372736</a>"},{"pid":"1820a0c5bd9b4aa3151acc8ffd7ae88b603927b8","tid":446731,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb16406a057a347ae9988092b8cbb5b9e338437e","tid":446731,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"我以為係中國新聞"},{"pid":"1